data.title: 1919) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: James was born in Kentucky. He is with his parents, Thomas D and Narcissa, living with Thomas's parents Thomas P and Sarah or Sally (depending on the census) in Butler Co., Ky, in 1850, and again in 1860, although his father Thomas D is head of household, and his grandmother still lives in the household. siblings...
